						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up near a well on the way to Ponnavōlu.</p>						

						<p>It records the gift of land as <hi rend="italic">bhaṭṭayitu</hi> (Bhaṭṭavṛitti) mānyamu by the <hi rend="italic">sthānikas</hi> of the Ishṭakāmīśvara and Bhairavēśvara temple to Kāmarusu Timmayaṁgāru who has caused to construct a tank and channels at Ponnvōlu. In characters of about 17th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
